what_failed: Regression (0.92x): Isolated dimension table filters into separate CTEs using `materialize_cte` pattern and converted implicit joins to explicit JOIN syntax. This allows DuckDB to materialize highly selective dimension filters first, then join with the fact table using efficient hash joins.
why_it_failed: Pre-filtered and joined store_sales to date CTE BEFORE the 3-way fact table join (store_sales <- store_returns <- catalog_sales). By materializing the date-filtered store_sales early, the optimizer loses the ability to push filters across the multi-way fact join and reorder joins optimally.
